-- Methodology
-- Repos were identified through these sources:
--   1. Direct outreach to known ecosystem partners and community contributors
--   2. Midnight Foundation team and staff personal repos
--   3. GitHub code search for "pragma language_version" (Compact (Midnight's DSL) language
--      marker) 
--   4. GitHub topic and keyword searches:
--        - topic:midnightntwrk (official ecosystem topic tag)
--        - topic:compact midnight (Compact language topic)
--        - topic:midnight zk (midnight topic with ZK keyword filter)
--        - "midnight network" in:readme (exact phrase in repository readme)
--      All repos surfaced by these searches were manually reviewed for Midnight relevance before inclusion.
--
-- This is Midnight's first EC submission, ahead of mainnet launch.
-- Additional repos will be submitted in subsequent PRs as the ecosystem grows.
